    27	 * aside from configuration they are stateless; caching is implemented
    28	 * by other components.
    29	 *<p>
    30	 * Instances of this class are fully immutable as all configuration is
    31	 * done by using "fluent factories" (methods that construct new factory
    32	 * instances with different configuration, instead of modifying instance).
    33	 */
